  <p>â€œWhat Iâ€™m trying to tell you, in my own hamfisted way (God, Iâ€™m such an idiot!), is that you should, if you take my advice, go to that placeâ€”whatâ€™s it called? I forgetâ€”on Friday instead of â€¦ well, you know what Iâ€™m going to say â€¦ on Monday.â€</p>
