<blockquote>
  <p>â€œBefore you use the toaster, make sure you unplug the â€¦ well, it might not even be plugged in, but if it is, unplug the microwave, because if you use the toaster while itâ€™s plugged in â€¦ well, itâ€™s not like the house is going to blow up, butâ€¦â€</p>
