<ul>
  <li>â€œIâ€™m not saying you should get a dog, but if you do, which is not what Iâ€™m suggesting, youâ€™d probably like a German Shepherd â€¦ or maybe not. Who knows? I mean, itâ€™s your choice. But theyâ€™re great dogs. I mean, theyâ€™re not for everybody, but lots of people like them. In my experience.â€</li>
